snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS of ANIMALS that will make you DIE LAUGHING - Super FUNNY ANIMAL videos
snippet.description:
Animals are the best comedy! Watch this and you will laugh like hell! The ultimate try not to laugh challenge! Just look how all these dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, goats, horses,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
